{"tid":580782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝阿仙奴隊長在更衣室流淚：連我女兒都嫌我們爛","createTime":"2018-03-04T19:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T21:05:37.000Z","uid":161311,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"032fba94e674e4c81efae3b348e8de57c79f135f","tid":580782,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"最近阿仙奴可謂是風雨飄搖，連續的失敗讓他們成為了眾矢之的，而根據《衛報》的消息，在阿仙奴內部出現了的一幕，令人動容。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《衛報》的消息，週二的訓練課上，一名阿仙奴的年長球員在更衣室里發表了演講，在哽咽中，這名球員表示阿仙奴這支有天賦的球隊現在已經淪為了一堆漂流的垃圾。他的孩子甚至都在問他，為什麼阿仙奴現在這麼糟糕，當提到這件事時，這名球員的淚水充斥了眼眶。<br />\n<br />\n　　另一名阿仙奴球員站出來說：「我們是一家大球會，但是我們需要教練們更多的幫助。」其中有一名球員說：「這是不可能發生的，我們必須自己來找到解決的辦法。」<br />\n<br />\n　　後來《太陽報》記者Neil Ashton確認，這名落淚的球員是哥斯尼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8560597/7/20180304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F8560597%2F7%2F20180304&d=pEmv80Ww3uRh8MVoZrTHP0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=96b4a37f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8560597/7/20180304</a>"},{"pid":"ed72dc2f9af100e510facce477e636feb57ac492","tid":580782,"uid":2974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:05:59.000Z","msg":"漂流的垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153a42af422d013241acccb68e9ffafe2a617abb","tid":580782,"uid":134997,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:06:52.000Z","msg":"他知道 哭是沒有用的"},{"pid":"4d237403c93efa4be44ddfe3ff9008745bd56abc","tid":580782,"uid":12796,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:08:27.000Z","msg":"無可能 哥斯尼啞架"},{"pid":"27e92cc2cc434f25a1b8a2914f79930369ae7fdc","tid":580782,"uid":38286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:08:58.000Z","msg":"植物人"},{"pid":"b14ab62a480215b50c2fe946ffff48d150a8fd4d","tid":580782,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislik